<h1>QRCode()</h1>

<p>This plugin will create a QR Code image and return a image.</p>
<p><img src="https://bizonbytes.com/images/qrcode-bob.png"></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>Parameters added</p>
<table cellpadding="5">
  <thead>
    <tr>
      <th>Parameter</th>
      <th>Type</th>
      <th>Required</th>
      <th>Default</th>
      <th>Description</th>
    </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
    <tr>
      <td valign="top">linkTo</td>
      <td valign="top">string</td>
      <td valign="top">true</td>
      <td valign="top">&nbsp;</td>
      <td valign="top"><p>URL to link to. ex.: https://bizonbytes.com</p></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td valign="top">width</td>
      <td valign="top">string</td>
      <td valign="top">false</td>
      <td valign="top">150</td>
      <td valign="top">Width of QR Code image</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td valign="top">destination</td>
      <td valign="top">string</td>
      <td valign="top">false</td>
      <td valign="top">application.wheels.imagePath</td>
      <td valign="top">Where to save your image?</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td valign="top">filename</td>
      <td valign="top">string</td>
      <td valign="top">false</td>
      <td valign="top">qr</td>
      <td valign="top">Filename without the extension</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td valign="top">showImage</td>
      <td valign="top">boolean</td>
      <td valign="top">false</td>
      <td valign="top">true</td>
      <td valign="top">Do you want to show the image? No will only save the QR image file</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td valign="top">abortIfExist</td>
      <td valign="top">boolean</td>
      <td valign="top">false</td>
      <td valign="top">false</td>
      <td valign="top">Won't create the QR Code from google if the file already exist in your destination folder</td>
    </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>
<h2>Examples</h2>
<p><strong>From controller:</strong></p>
<p>&lt;cfset QRCodeImage(linkTo=&quot;https://bizonbytes.com&quot;, destination=&quot;/images/qrcodes&quot;,  showImage=&quot;false&quot;)&gt;</p>
<p><strong>From view:</strong></p>
<p>#QRCodeImage(linkTo=&quot;https://bizonbytes.com&quot;)&gt;#</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
